			<title>NetNewsWire 7.1b5</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
  				<ul>
				  <li>Made timeline scrolling faster and smoother
				  <li>Fixed bug (introduced in 7.0.6) where newly-arrived articles weren’t added to the search index
				  <li>Fixed a memory leak
				</ul>
			]]></description>
